{"id": 753, "genre": 1001, "title": "在被“我和微信的故事”刷屏后，你都做了啥？", "description": "从纠结前任到传谣辟谣的一个丰富的夜晚（插图来自：AGEN­TUR AZUR ）。", "record_count": 3362, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071945171kfM5q6b2AZm8Rn9.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-11T11:24:38Z", "options": [{"id": 40704, "content": "和闺蜜一起把时光拉回到大学。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246184}, {"id": 40705, "content": "截屏给第一个好友的时候 发现对方已经把你删了", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419324}, {"id": 40706, "content": "第一个好友是现在的好友“8楼A座”，特别感谢至今还是朋友，尽管不在一起，我希望友谊可以得到长存。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417356}, {"id": 41231, "content": "不看朋友圈！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356922}, {"id": 40726, "content": "静静看着爱凑热闹的人发图然后默默略过 估计没人会点赞 我就是我绝不凑热闹的烟火", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391846}, {"id": 40727, "content": "密码被老公改了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219212}, {"id": 40728, "content": "朋友太少不敢晒，也不知道h5在哪儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348735}, {"id": 40738, "content": "我朋友里居然还有转发这种消息的，好友地位果断下降一级", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403283}, {"id": 42020, "content": "只看喜欢的人的朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428319}, {"id": 40744, "content": "我立刻马上开始睡觉，卸载了微信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417806}, {"id": 40745, "content": "把支付宝的钱转走?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213748}, {"id": 40752, "content": "我都不知道那是啥，就被刷屏了。我当机了～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416434}, {"id": 40753, "content": "一直很恐慌，觉得我支付宝里的钱很不安全。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419625}, {"id": 40754, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 418302}, {"id": 41270, "content": "静静地看着他们转发辟谣辟谣，再静静地等待事实的澄清、无事实依据的传谣居然是半数或多数人更在意的舆论", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423169}, {"id": 40762, "content": "昨晚的朋友圈先是发截图，然后打假，然后辟谣，看着大家的智商的程度，心理蛮满足的，厚厚（别打我???）", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419690}, {"id": 40765, "content": "紅紅火火恍恍惚惚～第一個好友已經結婚啦，而我還只是一隻大一狗。ｖ（＾＿＾ｖ）♪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413144}, {"id": 42301, "content": "我就觉得现在微信跟微博把我困在一个让我反感的空间里。分享过盛，期待过盛，所以昨天我把微信跟微博删了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429741}, {"id": 40766, "content": "微信隨便一個什麼東西就能掀起網絡口水戰 足以說明現實生活中人都不會說話啦 所有言語都獻給屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408949}, {"id": 41024, "content": "没点开看过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272649}, {"id": 40774, "content": "My first friend is my best friend.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419783}, {"id": 40778, "content": "我什么也没做！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419833}, {"id": 40783, "content": "我就呵呵呵了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419130}, {"id": 41552, "content": "神马都没干", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425394}, {"id": 40790, "content": "也许能一直记得他是第一个好友，就不会好友变路人了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256232}, {"id": 41046, "content": "所以说朋友圈很无脑很无聊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 421039}, {"id": 40798, "content": "不停刷屏，等更多的秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267121}, {"id": 41320, "content": "打开的速度那叫一个慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256316}, {"id": 41074, "content": "根本看不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 421250}, {"id": 41331, "content": "静静地看你们装逼，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423662}, {"id": 41354, "content": "其实心里知道，朋友圈80%都是没用的或者不感兴趣的信息，除了已经慢慢成为一种习惯以外，就是想多保留一些可能性，也许你很烦的推销代购和心灵鸡汤哪天就会用的到，再来就是上新的朋友和极为关注的的人，心里会有些小期待。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399992}, {"id": 44690, "content": "冷漠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444940}, {"id": 40601, "content": "对着已经是前任的“第一个好友”落下了桑心的泪水。", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 41113, "content": "我就看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 421804}, {"id": 40602, "content": "花了一晚上时间给现任解释第一个好友是谁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 284, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 40603, "content": "你和你第一个好友还联系吗？……联系着呢，她刚还揍了我儿子呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 466, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 40604, "content": "把传谣信谣的人设置“不看他们的朋友圈”", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 40605, "content": "根本不理解这玩意儿有什么好截屏晒出来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 729, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 42399, "content": "卸载微信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430361}, {"id": 40869, "content": "觉定16年关闭朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414803}, {"id": 40618, "content": "小编是不是选错模版了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346805}, {"id": 40619, "content": "转发辟谣文章打脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268216}, {"id": 40621, "content": "默默关手机备战期末考", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336657}, {"id": 40624, "content": "流言止于智者，流言始于吃饱了撑着没事闲的慌??", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269364}, {"id": 41392, "content": "第一个联系人不是我，这不重要，居然还晒认识八年了。。。拜托，我们三个都是初中同学好不好，我一直那么重视你，到头来我还不如你养的那只猫\n初中毕业时说过不会忘记我，我真是有够天真才会相信你的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423984}, {"id": 40625, "content": "默默的全点了个赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333832}, {"id": 40626, "content": "发朋友圈辟谣", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122174}, {"id": 40627, "content": "马上去帮第一个好友点了个赞！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333832}, {"id": 40628, "content": "看看朋友圈里的哪个好友智商过低", "image": null, "praise_count": 172, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 6408}, {"id": 40884, "content": "很少发朋友圈了，发什么内容都觉得log", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 84017}]}